<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Balmy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Balmy,</orth> 1) full of medicinal power: <cit><quote>with the drops of this most b. time my love looks fresh,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 107.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 107, 9</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>b. slumbers,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.258" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 258</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) fragrant: <cit><quote>b. breath,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 16</bibl></cit>.
